---
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
            <div class="text-center fade-in-up">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-khoalan-yellow/10 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-khoalan-yellow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Giá Cả Cạnh Tranh</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Luôn mang đến mức giá tốt nhất từ nhà máy, tối ưu chi phí cho công trình của bạn.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-khoalan-yellow/10 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-khoalan-yellow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Chất Lượng Đảm Bảo</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Sản phẩm chính hãng, đạt tiêu chuẩn chất lượng cao, bền bỉ với thời gian.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-khoalan-yellow/10 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-khoalan-yellow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 18H3c-.6 0-1-.4-1-1V7c0-.6.4-1 1-1h10c.6 0 1 .4 1 1v11"/><path d="M14 9h4l4 4v4h-8v-4h-4V9Z"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Giao Hàng Nhanh Chóng</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Hệ thống vận tải chuyên nghiệp, giao hàng tận nơi trên toàn tỉnh Lâm Đồng.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-khoalan-yellow/10 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-khoalan-yellow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="16" height="16" x="4" y="4" rx="2"/><rect width="6" height="6" x="9" y="9" rx="1"/><path d="M15 2v2"/><path d="M15 20v2"/><path d="M9 2v2"/><path d="M9 20v2"/><path d="M2 15h2"/><path d="M2 9h2"/><path d="M20 15h2"/><path d="M20 9h2"/><path d="M4 12H2"/><path d="M22 12h-2"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Công Nghệ Tiên Tiến</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Dây chuyền sản xuất hiện đại, đáp ứng mọi yêu cầu kỹ thuật khắt khe nhất.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section> 